"title": "9110: after-life",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9110",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Although the OT generally portrays this as a vague and shadowy existence, often associated with judgment, there are hints of the idea of resurrection to a fuller life which are developed in the NT. The NT points to judgment beyond death and to the believers' hope in resurrection, to a more complete enjoyment of God's presence and his blessings and to the promise of a new heaven and earth.</p>\n<h2>The after-life in the OT</h2>\n<h3>The grave as a place of silence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:17\">PSA 115:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:5\">PSA 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:9\">PSA 30:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:10-Ps88:11\">PSA 88:10–88:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:18\">ISA 38:18</a></p>\n<h3>The grave as a place of darkness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:21-Job10:22\">JOB 10:21–10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:9\">1SA 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:12\">PSA 88:12</a></p>\n<h3>The grave as a place of no return</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:8-Job7:10\">JOB 7:8–7:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:22\">JOB 16:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:4\">PSA 146:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:18-Prov2:19\">PRO 2:18–2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:7\">ECC 12:7</a></p>\n<h3>The grave as a place of judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:5\">PSA 88:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:17\">PSA 31:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:18\">PRO 9:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:9-Isa14:11\">ISA 14:9–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:14\">ISA 26:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:14\">EZK 31:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek32:17-Ezek32:32\">EZK 32:17–32:32</a></p>\n<h3>The grave offers peace to the righteous</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:13\">JOB 3:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:2\">ECC 4:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:1-Isa57:2\">ISA 57:1–57:2</a></p>\n<h3>The hope of resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:26\">JOB 19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:10-Ps16:11\">PSA 16:10–16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:15\">PSA 49:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:24\">PSA 73:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:7-Isa25:8\">ISA 25:7–25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:19\">ISA 26:19</a></p>\n<h2>The after-life and God's judgment</h2>\n<h3>Judgment beyond death is certain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:27\">HEB 9:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:10\">2CO 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12-Rev20:13\">REV 20:12–20:13</a></p>\n<h3>There will be salvation for believers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:19-Matt25:23\">MAT 25:19–25:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:18\">REV 11:18</a></p>\n<h3>There will be separation from God for unbelievers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:15\">REV 20:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:27\">REV 21:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:12\">MAT 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:42\">MAT 13:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:13\">MAT 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:51\">MAT 24:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:30\">MAT 25:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:46\">LUK 12:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:15\">REV 22:15</a></p>\n<h2>The believing dead are already with Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:43\">LUK 23:43</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:14-1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:14–4:17</a></strong> <em>Believers, with Jesus Christ in spirit, await their final resurrection which will take place when he returns.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:3\">JHN 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:8\">2CO 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:23\">PHP 1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:23\">HEB 12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:9-Rev6:11\">REV 6:9–6:11</a></p>\n<h2>The after-life and believers' hope of resurrection</h2>\n<h3>The bodily resurrection of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:39-Luke24:43\">LUK 24:39–24:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:20\">JHN 20:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:26-John20:27\">JHN 20:26–20:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:3\">ACT 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1\">1JN 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Believers share in Christ's resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:14\">1CO 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:20-1Cor15:23\">1CO 15:20–15:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:14\">2CO 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>The resurrection body of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:20-Phil3:21\">PHP 3:20–3:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:23\">1CO 15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42-1Cor15:55\">1CO 15:42–15:55</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1-2Cor5:4\">2CO 5:1–5:4</a></p>\n<h2>The future consummation of the believers' enjoyment of God</h2>\n<h3>Future glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18-Rom8:19\">ROM 8:18–8:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17-2Cor4:18\">2CO 4:17–4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>A new heaven and earth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1\">REV 21:1</a></p>\n<h3>God's presence with his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2-Rev21:7\">REV 21:2–21:7</a></strong> <em>The final consummation will bring God's promises to and purposes for his people to fulfilment</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14\">REV 22:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:8\">EXO 25:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1-Rev22:5\">REV 22:1–22:5</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit as a guarantee</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:5\">2CO 5:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a></p>",
